COMMENT_TX: $popup dropped in CF; Willie McGee knocked it down
Defensive shift; 2B playing on 3B side of 2B

ej,youmf001,P,davib902,Throwing ball at umpire $Pitcher Youmans ejected by HP umpire Davidson for throwing ball at umpire who wanted to check it for damage after being hit off wall; this occurred as was being replaced by new pitcher; Youmans was unhappy over balls and strikes calls
$Phil Garner picked off but Jason Thompson threw it away

ej,rodgb102,M,palld901,Balls and strikes $Jeff Reardon was unhappy with the strike zone; as he left the field, HP umpire Dave Pallone walked to Reardon and the two argued; Expos manager Buck Rodgers came out to protect his pitcher and was ejected by Pallone
$Bill Madlock charged but bunt went over his head
$Vance Law safe when Pete Rose's throw hit him
$delay because of power failure in stadium
$Andres Galarraga nailed on pitch out on squeeze attempt
$Bob Kipper left with tight left shoulder
$Tim Raines sprained left wrist; removed later
ej,venam001,P,ripps901,fair/foul call $Reds Venable, not in game, ejected by 3B umpire Rippley for arguing that Law's triple was foul
$Hubie Brooks' throw went into the dugout

umpchange,6,umphome,monte901 umpchange,6,ump3b,rennd901 suspended,19860724,CIN08,rain $game suspended due to rain; completed July 24 in Cincinnati with 3B umpire Ed Montague behind the plate, Dutch Rennert at 3B and Steve Rippley out of the game
$Mitch Webster lost it in the sun
$Tim Wallach and Bob Horner collide; Horner left game later
$Vance Law's relay throw hit Andres Thomas
ej,dyksl001,P,bonig901,Balls and strikes Lenny Dykstra ejected by HP umpire Greg Bonin for arguing strike call on 1-2 count
Andy Van Slyke hurt his thumb on the play
ej,rodgb102,M,demud901,Interference call $Luis Rivera called for interference; Expos manager Buck Rodgers ejected by HP umpire Dana DeMuth
$Randy Hunt missed tag on Chili Davis then threw wild to 3B
$Vance Law injured himself on the play
Rob Thompson hit on hand; removed after first
